name: SIGIL OF THE SKY
description:
Between the heavens and the soil humans rule their mighty kingdoms enveloped by a sea of clouds and sun. We, on earth, look to the sky in search for answers, in search of comfort, in prayer, in awe, in hopeful dreaming of better days.
Lay under the sunny sky and let yourself go to dreams of a future past.

800x800gif made on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
